EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Get The Most Out Of Your Digital Advertising
Thank you for your interest in Adforms products. It's important to us that you're having the best possible experience with Adform.
If you would like a demo with one of our specialists, please reply to this e-mail. In the meantime, here are more resources on how Adform helps agencies maximize the effectiveness of their advertising spend.
Watch our full stack advertising platform show reel or join our Global Creative Solutions Lead, David Hillier, on The Art and Science of Storytelling: How to Build Technology Empowered Ads to Create Vivid Narratives.
Make sure to check out our Knowledge base if you would like to find out more about our latest research, more detailed information about our products, or register for one of our free webinars.
{!Lead.OwnerFullName}
Adform has grown at an amazing pace in the last 5 years. Starting as an ad-server, it now represents a best-in-class AdTech solution: a tech giant with an entrepreneurial flavour when it comes to customization. Partnering with Adform gave our agency a competitive advantage in the Italian advertising market.
Sandro Moretti, President of Simple Agency (Dentsu Group)
